{"tid":2528855,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"譚仔三哥殺入蘭桂坊 承租前翠華巨舖 料今季開張","createTime":"2021-05-13T10:26:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-14T19:29:59.000Z","uid":162944,"like":104,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"00f948d72b461ae85f243a22d853530e40431f38","tid":2528855,"uid":162944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-13T10:26:00.000Z","msg":"譚仔國際宣布，承租中環威靈頓街15-19號香港工商大廈地庫及地面兩層，面積約4,000方呎，計劃開設中環區首間譚仔三哥米線，滿足顧客殷切需求，新店料於第二季投入市場。<br />\n<br />\n翻查資料，該舖位曾由翠華（1314）自1998年租用22年，地庫、地下、閣樓及1樓總面積約8160方呎，曾是「蒲友」聚腳地，惟去年不敵疫情結業。<br />\n<br />\n譚仔國際上月遞交上市申請，在港分別經營72間譚仔及譚仔三哥，不過中西區只有極少分店，更有譚仔三哥粉絲開設名為「為何中西區沒有譚仔三哥」的fb專頁。譚仔於去年11月進駐中環，新店樓高3層，而譚仔三哥同月亦在上環開設新店，今次將是譚仔三哥首間位於中環的分店。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/fin/20210513/s00010/f0135baa0e4e4ee3d8539717f78be640.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2F20210513%2Fs00010%2Ff0135baa0e4e4ee3d8539717f78be640.jpg&h=a706850f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1620894152258&amp;issue=20210513\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfinance.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1620894152258%26issue%3D20210513&d=q6lxkNJLkMCZuErjOs479I2ydpG6lAcy7lEd76f4zig%3D&h=fe574e1d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1620894152258&amp;issue=20210513</a>"},{"pid":"adbe400d469b0af16453a6e0bf51865d5b45cf20","tid":2528855,"uid":308567,"like":80,"dislike":4,"score":76,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-13T10:27:18.000Z","msg":"喂 去三哥食個早餐"},{"pid":"6225d4632accffd52914b9540b33d0e44b6cdd04","tid":2528855,"uid":4239,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"quote":{"pid":"adbe400d469b0af16453a6e0bf51865d5b45cf20","tid":2528855,"uid":308567,"like":80,"dislike":4,"score":76,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-13T10:27:18.000Z","msg":"喂 去三哥食個早餐"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-13T10:28:59.000Z","msg":"開11點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p