irginia而不是我？是不是我的裙不夠短，襯衫的領口不夠低？<br />\n<br />\n我搖搖頭，將目光從低胸裝與土匪雞翼的超現實景像移開，打開當天的報紙，喝一口鴨血。 我已經展開了新的一天，而她們還停留在昨日。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-14T06:27:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZXQNBc17bksUMVvQbs6GAJQ6T2DvMRV8ps9H5ZYuzddv?filename=N69euLk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN69euLk.png&h=08d91888&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e18fa9fc3442f8480f3030bdda19a8e5d7ceecde","tid":2528855,"uid":103799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-14T07:26:01.000Z","msg":"今晚約左朋友落老蘭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"304e1f0931a86da605f433a5e16d240b9d62db61","tid":2528855,"uid":54800,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-14T07:37:25.000Z","msg":"譚仔三哥會唔會成為第一間開7*24 既米線舖...??<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n响老蘭Yo 完女, 然後去譚仔三哥照清楚先~~~<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7a3db4eddf75c8f40bcb621a6bac9354bfce389","tid":2528855,"uid":164500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-14T07:41:02.000Z","msg":"食住物丸米睇打交<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}